{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "幸村 第1话 努力！新的目标！",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "决定日出之国命运的\\n月读之战结束后不久",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大帅！来过几招吧！\\n幸儿给您展示一下修行的成果！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "幸儿，抱歉。\\n老夫今日另有安排，\\n实在腾不出时间陪你过招。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "唔……好吧。\\n既然如此……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "幸儿就在这里等大帅把事办完！\\n无论多少天都能等！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "倒是没那个必要……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "这次正好是个好机会，\\n你也陪老夫走一趟吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "好的！非常乐意！\\n所以……大帅接下来\\n是要去做什么啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "和修行差不多。\\n只不过要锻炼的不是老夫自己。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "而是要训练老夫麾下的士兵，\\n提高他们的作战能力。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "鹤翼阵！左右展开！\\n包围敌军！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "右阵！切莫急进！\\n阵型都乱了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "幸儿啊……演练很无聊吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "诶！？不是！\\n没、没那回事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "只是觉得大军作战\\n让人看着有点着急……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "感觉大帅您自己突击\\n会更快些……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "噢？你为什么会这么认为？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "因为凭大帅您的本事，\\n像这种普通的士兵\\n根本不是您的对手啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "武艺的最高境界是万夫莫当！\\n大帅一人就能把\\n千人大军杀得片甲不留！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "原来你是这么想的……\\n那如果对手也和老夫一样，\\n是万夫莫当的强者呢？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "诶？可、可是，\\n能和大帅您匹敌的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "也不能说没有对吧。\\n还记得不久前那一战吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "嗯……幸儿记得很清楚。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "当时多亏有\\n尤蒂尔殿下相助\\n才能化险为夷。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "但那样的强者可不会\\n每次都能凑巧前来援助。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110040_101"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "月读一事让幕府陷入了混乱。\\n也许会有反抗幕府或龙氏的\\n势力趁此机会作乱……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "为了守护日出之国的安宁，\\n我们十二龙氏必须时刻磨练自己！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大帅，幸儿也是这个想法！\\n所以幸儿才要为了\\n变得更强而继续修……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "只是这样还不够！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "不够！？\\n您是说……\\n幸儿的努力和毅力还不够吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "不。你身为人，已经足够强大。\\n但身为将，却还远远不够。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "身为将？\\n这是什么意思啊，大帅？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "龙氏可以以一敌千……\\n那么反过来讲，千人大军\\n便等同于一位龙氏。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "若能如臂使指般指挥千人大军，\\n那就意味着……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "就、就意味着！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "战场之上多了一位龙氏！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "啊！原来如此……\\n的确是这样！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "这便是身为将的能力。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "据老夫所知，家康正在为了\\n应对可能到来的威胁而操练军队，\\n还展现出了优秀的指挥能力……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "而老夫也打算锻炼信玄军，\\n让他们能够对抗任何对手。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "所以……信玄军听令！\\n摆方圆阵！动作要快！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "（不愧是大帅……\\n思考竟如此深远！）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "（原本以为自己身为武士\\n已经可以与大帅相提并论……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "（没想到身为武将\\n却还远远不及大帅……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "（幸儿一定要追上大帅的脚步！\\n一定要像大帅那样，\\n如臂使指地指挥大军！）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "在那之后，回到领地的幸村\\n开始学习兵法，然而……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "鹤……鹤……翼阵？\\n为了包……包围敌人而……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "啊～啊……不行啊，\\n一打开书就感觉头晕……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "既然如此，看幸儿临场发挥！\\n管他三七二十一，冲就是了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大伙！冲呀！\\n一口气包围敌人！\\n一口气消灭敌军！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "咦！？怎么队伍各走各的……\\n不对不对，不是那边！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "啊～啊……\\n完全指挥不来啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大帅真厉害啊。\\n到底要怎样才能像大帅\\n那样指挥军队呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "不行！幸儿，你不能气馁！\\n不能就此放弃！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "只要凭努力和毅力……\\n就一定能够成功！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}